data.description: Stunning home in the highly sought after community of Canyon Trails! Discover the beauty & durability of wood-like flooring and plantation shutters that enhance elegance in every room of this split floorplan. Entertain family and friends in the expansive great room, perfect for gatherings and cozy nights. The kitchen is a chef's dream with a huge pantry & butler area, sleek black & matte black appliances, gorgeous granite counters, large kitchen island, upgraded white cabinets, door pulls, soft close drawers/cabinets, glass cooktop, double oven, and tons of storage!  Work from home in style! The large office features French frosted glass doors, windows over looking the front yard and upgraded Wi-Fi network for reliable internet connectivity. Retreat to your primary bedroom spa-like oasis, double door entrance, an oversized walk-in shower featuring tile and stylish glass door, and massive closet provides ample space for all your wardrobe needs.  Say good-bye to cramped spaces! The spacious laundry room boasts a utility sink, counter, and cabinets, making chores a breeze. Convenience is key, the garage has a door leading to the back yard in this beautiful north/south facing home.  Nearby several parks, neighborhood pool, shopping, dining, and hiking.  Welcome home!
